{
  "stem": "6258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at this time, for about a year, we had the nice free life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However, we were very different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We, who were in Krakow, were told very soon that there will be a ghetto in Krakow, but that ghetto where the Germans did, it was not in this part of Krakow, which was traditionally, well, Jewish, where Jews lived there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We did not live in this, we were in a different part.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they decide to make in the poorest section of Krakow, and therefore, well, when it came the day when we were supposed to move there it looked really strange.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On one side of the street you saw masses of people coming from this part to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On the other side of the street, masses of people coming from Krakow to this part where was supposed to be ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were just a few streets, not too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a very small place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in the middle of the streets, it was all one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The day we had to be in the ghetto was about, I think, 18 or, or so of March, 1941.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this was-- at this time it was quite a long notification, I think about two weeks or so, because they had to take care of this people who were not Jewish in this part of Krakow where the ghetto was, to relocate them.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so therefore, it was not just two days or three days, no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had, like, platform wagon, and well, from four or five rooms you could take just the most important things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but that part of our things what we had, we couldn't take with us, we give to our nanny.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, for example, this carpet she had.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
